{"tid":1126686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幽默鏡頭下的擠迫香港：德國攝影師辭世，終年65歲","createTime":"2019-04-26T14:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T17:46:31.000Z","uid":164771,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c33339e9cff8185e322a910b918cbefbc91887","tid":1126686,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2019/04/c306738bb838403fa2042562f21f4572.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2019%2F04%2Fc306738bb838403fa2042562f21f4572.JPG&h=13f71fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2019/04/9f752471acc1412a9436df67638cd550.JPG?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/1350/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2019%2F04%2F9f752471acc1412a9436df67638cd550.JPG%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F1350%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=96fb9be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2019/04/a839010f269742c2bd7dfd2dc009af21.JPG?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/864/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2019%2F04%2Fa839010f269742c2bd7dfd2dc009af21.JPG%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F864%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=a2a04c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國攝影師兼藝術家 Michael Wolf 昨日（4月25日）於香港長洲家中離世，享年65歲。曾與 Michael Wolf 合作舉行回顧展的荷蘭海牙攝影博物館（Fotomuseum Den Haag）較早前宣布了這項消息。<br />\n<br />\nMichael Wolf 出生於德國慕尼黑，成長於美國及加拿大，他在1994年成為攝影記者，為德國雜誌《Stern》工作而來到香港，其後在香港定居。Wolf 擅長以冷冽的攝影風格捕捉香港獨特的密集城市景觀，衝擊觀眾視覺，其中以攝影集《Architecture of Density》(2003 &ndash; 2014)最為人所認識。另外，他又以其細微觀察和幽默的拍攝手法，創造多項以香港公共空間為主題的攝影作品，包括吸煙的後巷肖像、窄巷的植物、街上神位等。<br />\n<br />\nWolf 是國際攝影獎項的常客。2005年他以中國玩具廠為主題的作品《The Real Toy Story》獲得世界新聞攝影大賽（World Press Photo）「當代議題」類別一等獎。2010年，他以黑色幽默的角度捕捉東京上班族於地鐵車廂擠得面容扭曲的《Tokyo Compression》系列，在同一個比賽中的「日常生活」類別獲得一等獎。2011年，他以拍攝 Google 街景記錄下來的意外場景，再獲當代問題組別榮譽獎。<br />\n<br />\nWolf 年前接受媒體訪問時說，他特別喜歡拍下城市裏被忽略的景象，更愛收集在橫街窄巷中找到的物件，因為他能夠從中找到香港的獨特文化和身份、看到人與城市之間的關係。Wolf 表示他對香港人的身份議題特別感興趣，無奈這身份逐漸被中國大陸慢慢同化，失去原有的特色。<br />\n<br />\n「我拍照，就是希望將這些非常地道的文化紀錄下來。」<br />\n<br />\n原文：《幽默鏡頭下的擠迫香港：德國攝影師Michael Wolf辭世，終年65歲》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20190426-photo-michaelwolf/?fbclid=IwAR3EB3cmZBNWOqNGNpKOnfFRgZL09m9Pv_4t8Hdk-hBCp-wNJCMT5L6qut4&amp;utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20190426-photo-michaelwolf%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3EB3cmZBNWOqNGNpKOnfFRgZL09m9Pv_4t8Hdk-hBCp-wNJCMT5L6qut4%26utm_medium%3Dcopy&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjiF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=4dde658a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20190426-photo-michaelwolf/?fbclid=IwAR3EB3cmZBNWOqNGNpKOnfFRgZL09m9Pv_4t8Hdk-hBCp-wNJCMT5L6qut4&amp;utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media"},{"pid":"0e35419c7f2d1c3087210e2bdd3a09fdec52f887","tid":1126686,"uid":10692,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa7c65f940d52da3643cf95b0f67ef58e422772d","tid":1126686,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T15:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e128b627231b93ec7dcb99b21749a786ac8836","tid":1126686,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"證明香港唔係人住...."}]}